blogs.title: Game Requests, 5/27/19
blogs.text:
How to suggest a game for this site.
1. Determine if it is possible to put on a site. EX: I probably could not host Fortnite on this site.
2. Find a web location where this game is found online.
3. Email me the logistics of the of the game, such as the site it is found on, to jeffastedman@gmail.com.
4. Do not expect every game you suggest to go in this site, I'm not perfect and some games may be inapropriate.
